This file is the LICENSE for the livespec-authored `jsoncomment` shim
under .claude-plugin/scripts/_vendor/jsoncomment/. The shim is a
derivative work of jsoncomment 0.4.2 (Gaspare Iengo, MIT-licensed),
faithfully replicating that release's `//` and `/* */` comment-stripping
semantics. The canonical upstream
(https://bitbucket.org/Dando_Real_ITA/json-comment) was sunset by
Atlassian; the PyPI sdist (https://pypi.org/project/jsoncomment/) is the
only surviving source-of-record.

The MIT license text below applies to both jsoncomment 0.4.2 (the
upstream original, copyright Gaspare Iengo) and the livespec-authored
derivative shim.

